How to install (the flags are optional):

$ ./configure --prefix=/usr
$ make
# make install

If you have problems with dependencies resolution,
and you are sure they are there, try the following:

rm -rf ~/.wafcache

Homepage: http://fama-im.org
Irc channel: irc.freenode.net #fama

Contributions are welcome!
This file will have something more useful in the future :)
